Class Vertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • Vertex

  • public class Vertex
extends java.lang.Object
    The Vertex Class creates a single Vertex (a circle) on the Bridg-it gameboard. A Vertex object has the following properties (instance variables): 1. the (x,y) identifier on the Bridg-it graph, which looks like a 4*5 or 5*4 grid 2. the position on the GUI canvas 3. the size of the corresponding circle on the GUI 4. whether the Vertex has been used by the user (for forming an edge) 5. the neighboring area of the Vertex on the GUI
    Version:
    (12/13/18)
    Author:
    (Jane Yang, Yining Li, Caiqin Zhou)
